"e-n-accordion-item-1130\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-991fb58 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"991fb58\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-601c1ab elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"601c1ab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Lorsqu\u2019une personne impos\u00e9e en France effectue un don pour la Fondation des Femmes, elle re\u00e7oit de fa\u00e7on automatique un re\u00e7u fiscal lui permettant de b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier d\u2019une r\u00e9duction fiscale de 75% , quel que soit son lieu de r\u00e9sidence.<\/p>\n<p>En revanche, pour les personnes impos\u00e9es \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tranger, le re\u00e7u fiscal d\u00e9livr\u00e9 ne sera valable qu\u2019aupr\u00e8s de l\u2019administration fran\u00e7aise.<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/details>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"loop-item\" data-elementor-id=\"15227\" class=\"elementor elementor-15227 e-loop-item e-loop-item-16704 post-16704 question type-question status-publish hentry\" data-elementor-post-type=\"elementor_library\" data-custom-edit-handle=\"1\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b257b8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3b257b8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c002c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion\" data-id=\"6c002c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;all_collapsed&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}\" data-widget_type=\"nested-accordion.default\">\n\t\t\t\t