\t\t\t\t<\/summary>\n\t\t\t\t<div role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"e-n-accordion-item-1130\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-991fb58 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"991fb58\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-601c1ab elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"601c1ab\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>En dehors des journ\u00e9es de collecte, nous ne sommes malheureusement pas en mesure de r\u00e9cup\u00e9rer les dons de protections menstruelles.<br \/>\nEn revanche, vous pouvez consulter\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/collectes.regleselementaires.com\/map\">les points de collecte pr\u00e8s de chez vous sur le site de l\u2019association R\u00e8gles \u00e9l\u00e9mentaires<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong>(notre partenaire associatif lors des journ\u00e9es d\u00e9di\u00e9es au sujet).<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/details>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"loop-item\" data-elementor-id=\"15227\" class=\"elementor elementor-15227 e-loop-item e-loop-item-16699 post-16699 question type-question status-publish hentry\" data-elementor-post-type=\"elementor_library\" data-custom-edit-handle=\"1\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b257b8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3b257b8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c002c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion\" data-id=\"6c002c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;all_collapsed&quot;,&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;one&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quo